snippet.title: STORY OF SEASONS: A Wonderful Life - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Direct 9.13.2022
snippet.description:
STORY OF SEASONS: A Wonderful Life is coming to Nintendo Switch in Summer 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/story-of-seasons-a-wonderful-life-switch/

A reimagining of the beloved classic title, STORY OF SEASONS: A Wonderful Life invites a new generation of players to work their own farms, grow their own families, and live their own wonderful lives in this peaceful farm sim.

#SOSWonderfulLife #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch
